<para style="p">

  <verse number="13" style="v" />We do not want you to misunderstand, brothers, about those who sleep, so that you do not grieve like the rest who do not have certainty about the future.

  <verse number="14" style="v" />For if we believe that Jesus died and rose again, just so God will bring with Jesus those who have fallen asleep in him.

  <verse number="15" style="v" />For this we say to you by the word of the Lord, that we who are alive, who are left at the coming of the Lord, will surely not precede those who have fallen asleep.
